{
  "text": "Now before the veil, an entity would be aware that he was experiencing a disease. As an example, would you give me, if you are aware of a case of a disease an entity might experience prior to the veil, and how he would react to this and think about it and what effect it would have on him in a complete sense. Would you could you give me an example, please? Hi. Inasmuch as the universe is composed of an infinite array of entities. There is also an infinity of response to stimulus. If you will observe your peoples, you will discover a greatly variant responses to the same distortion towards disease. Consequently, we cannot answer your query with any hope of making any true statements since the overgeneralizations required are too capacious.",
